    public static final Spell augury = new Spell("Augury", 2, "", "1 minute", 0, "v,s,m (specially marked sricks, bones, or other 25+gp tokens", "instant", "", "Using the material component as a divining tool you receive divine direction about specific course of action you'll take in the next 30 minutes. Can result in: Weall (good result), woe (bad result), weal & woe (mixed results), nothing (neither particularly good or bad). Doesn't account for changing circumstances. Repeated castings in 24 hrs gives cumulative 25% chance to give random result from dm.");
